          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-1" n="1">1<lb/>Here Sarum Lies</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-2" n="2">Of late so wise,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-3" n="3">And learned as Thomas Aquinus:</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-4" n="4">Lawn Sleeves He wore,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-5" n="5">Yet was no more</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-6" n="6">A Christian than Socinus.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-7" n="7">2<lb/>Oaths Pro &amp; Con</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-8" n="8">He swallow'd down,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-9" n="9">Lov'd Gold like any Layman:</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-10" n="10">Wrote, preach'd &amp; pray'd,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-11" n="11">But yet betray'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-12" n="12">Gods holy Church for Mammon.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-13" n="13">3<lb/>Of Ev'ry Vice</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-14" n="14">He had a Spice,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-15" n="15">Altho a Rev'rend Prelate;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-16" n="16">Yet liv'd and died,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-17" n="17">If not bely'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-18" n="18">A true dissembling Zealot.</l>
            <l rend="center indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-19" n="19">4<lb/>If such a Soul</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-20" n="20">To Heav'n should strole,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-21" n="21">And 'Scape old Satan's Clutches:</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-22" n="22">We may presume</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-23" n="23">there will be Room</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y49-261O-line-24" n="24">For M──·── &amp; his Dutchess.</l>
